Dialogue: 0,0:00:10.46,0:00:14.96,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,（六个月后）
Dialogue: 0,0:00:18.22,0:00:20.76,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,两列火车 两个不同的篇章\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}- Two trains, two chapters to tell.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:24.06,0:00:25.72,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,一列高速飞驰\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}One runs hot and fast.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:30.31,0:00:31.90,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,另一列蹒跚而行\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}The other lumbers slow...
Dialogue: 0,0:00:34.44,0:00:36.69,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那是威尔福德铁腕掌控下的列车\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Cold-cast in Wilford's iron grip...
Dialogue: 0,0:00:38.57,0:00:41.03,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,一只在兔子身后策划阴谋的 武装的乌龟\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}An armored tortoise plodding after a hare...
Dialogue: 0,0:00:42.32,0:00:43.99,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,所有人都受同一个人控制\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Everyone under a single thumb...
Dialogue: 0,0:00:45.62,0:00:47.37,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,服务于同一个偏执的目标…\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Serving a single obsession...
Dialogue: 0,0:00:49.58,0:00:52.92,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,夺回被盗的东西 实施他的报复\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}To retake the pirates and exact his revenge.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:53.96,0:00:55.21,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我能闻到他们的气味\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}I can smell them.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:56.46,0:00:58.51,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,从结冰情况来看\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Layton took my engine through here
Dialogue: 0,0:00:59.72,0:01:03.05,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,大约一个月前 雷顿把我的机车带到这里来过\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}about a month ago, judging by the ice buildup.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:03.72,0:01:05.22,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我们已经紧随其后了\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Practically on their heels.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:06.97,0:01:08.02,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,看到没 \N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}You see?
Dialogue: 0,0:01:08.10,0:01:10.18,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就像雪地里的足迹一样\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Like old footprints in the snow.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:11.48,0:01:13.56,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,工程师 转到往南去的岔路上\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Set switch for the south fork, Engineer.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:14.44,0:01:18.07,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我们会把它夺回来的 朱庇特 不惜任何代价\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}We'll get it back, Jupe, whatever it takes.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:20.19,0:01:23.78,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,列车鸣汽笛
Dialogue: 0,0:01:23.86,0:01:27.49,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,催人眼迷离
Dialogue: 0,0:01:27.58,0:01:31.04,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,男孩女孩们
Dialogue: 0,0:01:31.12,0:01:34.75,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,钻进毯子里
Dialogue: 0,0:01:34.83,0:01:38.46,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,司机伴引擎
Dialogue: 0,0:01:38.55,0:01:42.05,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,消防员按铃
Dialogue: 0,0:01:42.13,0:01:45.64,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,睡魔摇灯笼
Dialogue: 0,0:01:45.72,0:01:49.56,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,一切都安宁
Dialogue: 0,0:01:49.64,0:01:53.31,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,一路摇啊晃
Dialogue: 0,0:01:53.39,0:01:56.86,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,沿海湾启程
Dialogue: 0,0:01:56.94,0:02:00.61,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,跋涉数千里
Dialogue: 0,0:02:00.69,0:02:04.20,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,开往晨光镇
Dialogue: 0,0:02:04.28,0:02:08.08,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,列车途经处
Dialogue: 0,0:02:08.16,0:02:11.62,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,或许在下雨
Dialogue: 0,0:02:11.70,0:02:14.50,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,所有小旅客…
Dialogue: 0,0:02:14.58,0:02:16.46,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,列车里是一个倒退的世界\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}- Inside, it's a backwards world.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:17.46,0:02:18.75,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,如今只有一个阶级了\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Only one class now,
Dialogue: 0,0:02:20.21,0:02:21.84,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那就是工人阶级\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}the working class, freezing, stitching,
Dialogue: 0,0:02:21.92,0:02:25.93,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,缝补修葺 忍冻受罪\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}fixing, suffering.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:27.22,0:02:34.10,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,跋涉数千里 开往晨光镇
Dialogue: 0,0:02:42.19,0:02:43.90,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嘿 这里不是过道 \N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}- Hey, this isn't a pass-through.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:52.83,0:02:54.83,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,-温妮佩 -有给头儿捎的信\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}- Winnipeg. - Message for the top.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:02.09,0:03:04.05,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不过 挨冻的人们更会抱作一团\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}- But frostbitten fingers hold fast.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:06.01,0:03:09.30,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在寒冰深处 威尔福德从不涉足的地方\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Deep in the iced-over bowels where Wilford never treads...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:12.47,0:03:13.89,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,依然有一丝火花在闪耀\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}A spark still lives:
Dialogue: 0,0:03:15.18,0:03:16.35,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那就是抵抗军\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}the resistance,
Dialogue: 0,0:03:17.14,0:03:20.44,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,由勇者中的勇者培养并守护着\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}nurtured and protected by the bravest of the brave.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:25.95,0:03:27.74,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,给头儿捎的信\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}- Message for the tippity-top.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:29.57,0:03:31.70,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,派克先生 你没说暗号\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}- I didn't hear the password, Mr. Pike.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:31.78,0:03:33.99,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你是我的二把手 我对你的期望比这要高\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}I expect more from my second in command.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:34.79,0:03:36.58,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,他们发现了雪国列车的踪迹\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}They picked up sign of Snowpiercer.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:37.21,0:03:39.71,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我们已转向南面 回到了主轨道上\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}We turned south, back on the main line.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:40.21,0:03:41.42,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,谢天谢地\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Oh, thank God for that.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:42.75,0:03:48.47,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,32天了 这是第一个 证明他们还活着的消息\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}This is the first proof we've had that they are still alive in 32 days.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:48.55,0:03:51.80,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,他们这样到处闲转 一定有他们的原因\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}They must--they must have their reasons for all this traipsing about.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:51.89,0:03:53.06,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,如果梅兰妮在列车上的话\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}I mean, if Melanie's aboard--
Dialogue: 0,0:03:54.14,0:03:55.27,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这又说不定的\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}We don't know.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:57.60,0:04:01.44,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,鲁丝 晚上你一个人 待在这下面时 有没有想过\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}- You ever think, Ruth, all alone down here at night,
Dialogue: 0,0:04:01.52,0:04:03.90,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,既然当初是雷顿抛下了我们\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}that since Layton bailed on us in the first place,
Dialogue: 0,0:04:03.98,0:04:05.57,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,他可能永远都不会回来了 \N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}he might never come back?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:07.11,0:04:08.82,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,没想过\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}No, I don't.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:09.61,0:04:12.91,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你也没有 否则你不会加入抵抗军\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}And neither do you, or you wouldn't be in the resistance.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:12.99,0:04:17.45,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好了 这些抗生素给裁缝们 她们会需要的\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}- So antibiotics for the seamstresses. They'll need them,
Dialogue: 0,0:04:17.54,0:04:19.75,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,大家都挤在那个血汗工厂里\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}all jammed up together in that sweatshop.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:19.83,0:04:22.29,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这些小小的补给品能让我们保持理智\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}It's these little things that will keep us sane, Mr. Pike.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:22.38,0:04:25.30,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,如果我们能让旅途稍微舒服点 乘客们就能熬过这一关\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}The passengers can survive all of this if we can ease their journey.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:26.51,0:04:28.55,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,让他们为雷顿先生的归来做好准备\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}And keep them ready for Mr. Layton's return.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:30.72,0:04:34.68,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,威尔福德1023节车厢长的集中营 轰隆前行\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}- The heart of hope still beats aboard Wilford's rolling gulag,
Dialogue: 0,0:04:35.43,0:04:37.98,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在车上依然跳动着满怀希望的心\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}1,023 cars long.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:13.80,0:05:17.10,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好 这里应该不会有轨道污染物了\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Okay. Should be clear of track contaminants.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:17.72,0:05:19.68,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我要开始采集冰样了\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}I'm gonna start pulling ice samples.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:20.27,0:05:21.44,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,外面看上去怎么样 \N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}How's it looking?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:21.52,0:05:23.65,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,棕榈树 金沙滩\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}- Palm trees, golden sands.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:23.73,0:05:26.11,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我得去赶朝鲜的海浪\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Gotta catch me some North Korean waves.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:26.19,0:05:28.44,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真不错 我去拿一下冲浪板 马上就出去 兄弟\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}- Nice. I'll grab my board. I'll be right out, bro.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:28.53,0:05:29.36,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,让他集中精力\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}- Let him focus.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:29.44,0:05:31.70,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,-我是在帮他保持冷静 -你是在让他分心\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}- I'm keeping him calm. - You're distracting him.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:31.78,0:05:34.11,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,本 你的防护服还能坚持22分钟 你的心率正常\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}- Ben, the suit's at 22 minutes. Your heart rate's good.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:34.20,0:05:35.74,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不用紧张 好吗 \N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}You steady on, okay?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:35.82,0:05:36.87,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,收到\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Copy that.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:47.00,0:05:48.17,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,引擎运转得好点了吗 \N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Engine any happier?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:48.80,0:05:50.59,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在排放燃料 但还是过热\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}- We're venting, but still too hot.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:51.67,0:05:52.67,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,外面的情况如何 \N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}How's it looking?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:54.55,0:05:56.14,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,“零下86摄氏度”\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Oh, minus 86.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:56.80,0:05:59.14,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好吧 亏我们还大老远跑来这里\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Oh, well, I'm sure glad we came all this way.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:59.22,0:06:01.02,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,别把天气和气候的概念搞混了\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}- Well, don't mistake the weather for the climate.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:01.10,0:06:03.56,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,本采集的样本会显示气候的全貌\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Ben's samples will show us the full picture.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:03.64,0:06:05.06,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我们是在寻找趋势\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}We're looking for trends.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:05.15,0:06:07.27,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我还以为我们是在找宜居的地方\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}- I thought we were looking for a place to live.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:07.36,0:06:09.69,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,模型说这里是合适地点 等采样结果出来再说\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}The model likes this spot. Let's just wait for the results.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:09.78,0:06:10.61,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,“模型”\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Oh, the model.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:11.19,0:06:13.95,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嘿 提尔 还记得之前 模型说苏拉威西岛很合适吗 \N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}- Hey, Till, remember how much the model liked Sulawesi?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:14.03,0:06:15.57,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,记得\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Yeah, I do.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:15.66,0:06:18.53,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我们环行世界六个月了 却没拿得出手的成绩\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Six months of going around the world with nothing to show for it.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:18.62,0:06:20.37,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,每一次停留 我们都了解到了新信息\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}- And we learned something from every stop.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:20.45,0:06:22.91,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,-就把它们当作是数据点嘛 -行 雷顿教授\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Think of them as data points.  Okay, Professor Layton.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:23.00,0:06:26.83,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那些不是冰冻的地狱 而是数据点\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}- They were not frozen hellscapes. They were data points.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:26.92,0:06:27.92,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,没错\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Correct.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:38.43,0:06:39.35,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,糟糕\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Shit.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:39.43,0:06:40.81,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,（热敏开关故障）
Dialogue: 0,0:06:40.89,0:06:43.06,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,-我需要跟他通话 -好\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}- I need to talk to him. - Okay.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:44.60,0:06:47.65,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,本 主管道上的一个热敏开关坏了\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}- Ben, we just blew a thermal switch on the main line.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:47.73,0:06:50.02,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,-准是误报 -不是的\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}- It's gotta be an error. - It isn't.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:50.11,0:06:51.86,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我跟你说过 我们的空燃比太小了\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}We came in too rich. I told you that.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:51.94,0:06:55.36,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,把多余的燃料排出去就行 艾莉 引擎自己会调整的\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}- Just discharge the excess, Alex. She'll rebalance.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:55.45,0:06:58.20,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,若再继续排放燃料 我们就会启动不了了\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}If I discharge any more, we won't be able to get going again.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:58.82,0:07:00.87,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我们必须放弃行动 让他回来\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}We have to abort. Pull him in.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:01.41,0:07:04.33,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,别听她的 雷顿 她能调整好空燃比的\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}She's wrong, Layton. She can ride the levels.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:04.41,0:07:05.46,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,再给我十分钟\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Ten more minutes.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:05.54,0:07:08.13,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我们在大量耗费燃料 我们得马上启程\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}- We're burning up. We need to go right now.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:09.50,0:07:10.67,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,尽你所能稳住引擎\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Do what you can.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:11.75,0:07:13.63,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我跟他说了空燃比太小\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}- I told him we came in too rich.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:13.71,0:07:15.22,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好吧\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Okay.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:17.18,0:07:19.01,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,一切尽在掌握之中\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Everything's under control.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:19.09,0:07:21.39,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,本 你继续完成任务 好吗 \N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}- Ben, just stay on task. Okay?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:40.20,0:07:41.24,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗨\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Hey.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:41.33,0:07:42.66,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,她今天早上发过脾气吗 \N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}She touchy this morning?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:42.74,0:07:44.37,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,非常尖酸刻薄\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}- Scathing. So mean.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:45.75,0:07:47.62,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,-赛克斯马上就到 -很好\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}- Sykes is on her way. - Great.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:49.42,0:07:51.50,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我们为什么又停下了 \N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Why have we stopped again?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:52.96,0:07:55.05,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,他们找不到绿洲的 这你很清楚\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}You know, they're not gonna find an oasis. - You know that.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:55.13,0:07:58.22,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我什么都不清楚 这样更容易些\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}- I don't know anything. It's easier that way.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:58.30,0:08:01.85,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,跟谁都不熟 什么感觉都没有 我的囚犯 你是个孤独的女人\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}- Ugh, know no one, feel nothing. You're a woman alone, my jailer.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:01.93,0:08:03.35,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,至少我还有你\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Well, at least I got you.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:04.72,0:08:07.43,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你是想规规矩矩地在外面吃呢 还是想在里面吃 \N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}You gonna be civil, or do you want me to feed you in there?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:08.31,0:08:09.31,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,禽兽优先\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Monsters first.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:09.39,0:08:10.69,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,-不 请吧 -不要\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}- No, please. - No.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:10.77,0:08:14.98,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好了 能选的越来越少 这是今天的选择\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}- Okay. Today's dwindling selection.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:15.82,0:08:18.32,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我们有红酒炖牛肉\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}We have the boeuf bourguignon,
Dialogue: 0,0:08:18.40,0:08:21.57,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,培根蛋酱意面、可怕的蘑菇鸡肉套餐\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}the carbonara, the dreaded chicken mushroom bag,
Dialogue: 0,0:08:21.66,0:08:23.95,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,还有最后一份泰式蔬菜\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}and the last Thai vegetable.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:24.03,0:08:26.45,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,给这些铁路强盗干活 你好像挺开心\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}- You seem to enjoy working for these pirates.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:26.54,0:08:29.04,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,奥德丽 我只是个服刑中的战俘而已\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}- Just a POW doing my time, Audrey.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:29.12,0:08:31.38,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你这么配合他们 他会恶心死的\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}- Well, he'd be disgusted with your cooperation.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:31.46,0:08:33.09,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,能别拌嘴了吗 \N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Can you please?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:33.17,0:08:36.59,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,-如果没人想要泰式蔬菜… -马汀 给我培根蛋酱意面\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}- If nobody wants the Thai vegetable... - Just give me the carbonara, Martin.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:36.67,0:08:38.80,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,培根蛋酱意面是最难吃的\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Carbonara, it's the worst.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:41.93,0:08:45.56,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,本 风开始大了 看来有冷锋要来了\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}- Ben? Ben, the wind's picking up. It looks like there's a front coming in.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:45.64,0:08:47.85,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,收到 我这就回去\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}- Copy that. I'm on my way back.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:47.93,0:08:48.77,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,艾莉那里情况如何 \N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}- How's Alex?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:48.85,0:08:49.77,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,艾莉 汇报情况\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}- Alex, status.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:49.85,0:08:51.35,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,引擎没有着火\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}We're not actively on fire.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:52.35,0:08:53.23,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,让他动作快一点\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Tell him to hurry.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:53.81,0:08:56.48,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,她说她听了你的建议 一切运作正常\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}- She says she took your advice and everything's working out.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:59.49,0:09:01.20,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这里有很多飘雪\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}So much blown snow.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:01.28,0:09:03.07,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,有大量的风吹过这片盆地\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}A lot of wind comes through this basin.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:03.16,0:09:04.37,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这是好事 对吗 \N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}- Well, that's good, though, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:05.12,0:09:06.03,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,可能是\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Could be.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:06.12,0:09:08.75,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,可能是模型测到的暖点引起的\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Might be our warm spot stirring things up.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:27.93,0:09:29.52,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,（信号丢失）
Dialogue: 0,0:09:29.60,0:09:30.73,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,-本  -本 \N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}- Ben. - Ben?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:30.81,0:09:33.10,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,-本  -本 收到请回答 本\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}- Ben. - Ben, come in, Ben.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:33.81,0:09:35.31,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,-我看不到他了 -本 \N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}- I can't see him. - Ben.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:35.40,0:09:38.36,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,本 听到我说话了没 本 \N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}- Ben! Ben, do you copy? Ben.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:44.11,0:09:45.62,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,本 听到没有 \N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Ben, come in.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:01.05,0:10:03.05,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,贝丝 有件事我不明白\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}The bit I don't get, Bess,
Dialogue: 0,0:10:03.13,0:10:05.51,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,等把你们那宝贝气候模型 带回给威尔福德之后\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}when we return to Wilford with your precious climate model,
Dialogue: 0,0:10:05.59,0:10:06.43,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你们打算怎样 \N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}what happens then?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:07.18,0:10:08.35,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,谈判\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Negotiations.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:09.01,0:10:10.39,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,两列列车都想重新连接\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Both trains want to reconnect.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:10.47,0:10:12.60,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,没错 先谈交换人质的事\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}- Yeah. Hostage negotiations first.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:12.68,0:10:13.94,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,用你换扎拉\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}You for Zarah.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:15.27,0:10:16.94,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,行 然后呢 \N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}- Yeah, but then what?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:17.02,0:10:19.40,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,用你们这里的七个人 换威尔福德手里的2700个 \N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}- Wilford's 2,700 to your 7?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:19.48,0:10:22.15,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,对叛徒和偷渡者 他可不会客气\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}He's not gonna take too kindly to a traitor and a stowaway.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:22.24,0:10:23.20,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我怎么成偷渡者了 \N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}How am I a stowaway?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:23.28,0:10:26.11,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我当时在自己的车厢里打盹 醒来时列车已经不见了\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}I woke up from a nap in my carriage and the train was gone,
Dialogue: 0,0:10:26.20,0:10:28.58,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,连同我的老公和双胞胎儿子一起没了\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}along with my husband and my twin boys.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:28.66,0:10:29.49,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我是提尔\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Till here.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:29.58,0:10:31.37,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你得把他们关起来 然后到上面来\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}- Yeah, I need you to lock them down and get up here.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:31.45,0:10:33.71,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,-出什么事了  -没什么是他们需要知道的\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}- What's up? - Nothing they need to know about.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:33.79,0:10:35.12,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好 我这就去\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}- All right. On my way.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:35.21,0:10:36.96,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,本 听到没有 \N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Ben, do you read?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:37.04,0:10:39.46,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好了 午饭结束 马汀 把她关起来\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}All right, that's lunch. Martin, lock her up.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:39.54,0:10:41.25,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,-出什么事了吗  -动起来 快\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}- Is something wrong? - Move, go.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:45.05,0:10:48.47,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嘿 我之前看到本出去了 你们需要帮忙吗 \N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}- Hey, I saw Ben going outside earlier. - Do you need help?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:48.55,0:10:51.01,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不用 一切都好 我们没事\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}- No, everything's good. We're good.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:51.10,0:10:51.97,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这就去\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}On it.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:53.56,0:10:54.69,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,提尔 嘿\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}- Till. Hey,
Dialogue: 0,0:10:55.56,0:10:56.52,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,出什么事了 \N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}what's going on?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:56.60,0:10:58.56,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你们待在自己的房间里\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}You stay in your quarters.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:58.65,0:11:00.73,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,等着机车给出故障排除的指示\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Wait till the engine gives the all-clear.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:02.15,0:11:03.40,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,-就这样  -是的\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}- That's it? - Yep.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:14.08,0:11:16.29,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,-我要出去看看 -你不能去 我去\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}I'm going out there. - No, you're not. I'm going.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:16.37,0:11:18.21,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你们俩都不能出去\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}- Neither of you are going anywhere.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:18.29,0:11:20.46,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我们不能待在这里 本 \N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}We can't stay here. Ben.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:20.54,0:11:22.88,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,-本 听到了没  -我们不能撇下他\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Ben, do you copy? We are not leaving him.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:22.96,0:11:25.51,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,雷顿 如果现在不启动 引擎会烧坏的\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}- Layton, if we don't get rolling right now, we will melt down.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:25.59,0:11:26.84,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你需要多少时间 \N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}How long do you need?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:27.51,0:11:29.01,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,八分钟启动加速\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}- 8 minutes to get up to speed,
Dialogue: 0,0:11:29.09,0:11:31.30,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,10到12分钟运行燃料释放程序\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}10 to 12 minutes to run a discharge sequence.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:31.39,0:11:33.31,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,-很好 开始吧 -把你丢在外面吗 \N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}- Great. Go. - And leave you outside?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:33.39,0:11:36.31,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,抢修员的防护服能维持30分钟 你启动列车 然后再回来找我\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}- The breach suits have 30 minutes. You go, you come back for me.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:36.39,0:11:38.65,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,-你得留下 -听你的才怪\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}- You are staying here. - Yeah. Like, hell I am.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:43.11,0:11:44.11,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,没什么可讨论的\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}It's not a discussion, Josie.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:44.19,0:11:47.32,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,如果我们三个都出了事 就没人能完成户外任务了\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}If all three of us get in trouble out there, there's no one left for off-train work.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:47.40,0:11:49.49,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我会确保这情况不会发生\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}- Yeah, well, I'll make sure that doesn't happen.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:49.57,0:11:50.91,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就这么一次\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}- You know, one time,
Dialogue: 0,0:11:50.99,0:11:54.04,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,麻烦你改变一下习惯 服从指挥吧\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}just for a change of pace, you could respect the chain of command.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:55.08,0:11:56.29,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,“服从指挥” \N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Chain of command?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:57.04,0:12:00.04,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,雷顿 这不是艘战舰 而是个救生筏\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Layton, this isn't a battleship. It's a bloody life raft.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:00.13,0:12:01.21,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你得留在筏上\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}And you're staying on it.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:05.88,0:12:07.47,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,本根本就不该出去\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}- Ben shouldn't even be out there.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:07.55,0:12:10.55,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,-他知道自己在做什么 -是呀 追逐梅兰妮的鬼魂\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}- He knew what he was getting into. - Yeah. Chasing Melanie's ghost.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:10.64,0:12:11.64,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是验证她的理论\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Her theory.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:13.47,0:12:14.85,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我们都说好的\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}We all agreed.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:14.93,0:12:16.68,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,找到新伊甸园 再回去接大伙儿\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}We find New Eden, then we go back for the others.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:16.77,0:12:18.48,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,万一没有新伊甸园呢 \N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}- And what if there is no New Eden?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:19.31,0:12:20.65,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,万一她错了呢 \N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}What if she's wrong?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:23.48,0:12:25.36,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我们就跟她一起完蛋 \N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Guess we just all go down with her, eh?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:28.86,0:12:30.86,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,提尔 你得负责驾驶 把我们带出这里\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}- Till, you're gonna have to pilot us out of here.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:30.95,0:12:32.32,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我 为什么 \N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}- Me? Why?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:32.41,0:12:34.03,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,因为我得处理这个\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}- Because I need to go deal with that.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:34.12,0:12:35.12,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,什么 \N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}- What?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:35.87,0:12:36.91,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,老天\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Oh, Jesus. Jesus.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:38.04,0:12:40.00,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,行 好 交给我了\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Yeah, okay. I--I got it.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:46.13,0:12:48.51,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,（勿碰）
Dialogue: 0,0:12:48.59,0:12:50.30,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,（危险）
Dialogue: 0,0:12:53.85,0:12:56.77,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你那些天花乱坠的话 连自己都开始信了 你知道的吧 \N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}- You're starting to believe your own hype. You do know that, don't you?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:56.85,0:12:58.89,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我只是在努力让大家都活下去\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}- I'm just trying to keep everyone alive.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:58.98,0:13:01.98,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,对 我们知道 你是我们伟大的救世主\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Yep. We know. Our great savior.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:02.06,0:13:02.94,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我从没这么说过\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Never my words.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:03.56,0:13:06.57,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我从一开始就在末等车厢 脏的臭的我都经历过\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}- I was there at the beginning in The Tail, in the muck and the shit.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:06.65,0:13:08.19,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我知道你的为人\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}I know who you are.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:08.28,0:13:10.11,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,当初是你鼓励我当领袖的\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}- You encouraged me to be a leader.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:10.20,0:13:11.15,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不是领导这个\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}- Not for this.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:12.45,0:13:13.91,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这都不是我想要的\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Didn't ask for any of this.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:17.37,0:13:19.87,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,机车 我们在舱门口了 打开安全闸\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}- Engine, we're at the bay door. Release the safety.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:21.79,0:13:22.83,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,收到\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Uh, copy.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:22.92,0:13:24.46,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,舱门安全闸在哪儿 \N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Bay door safety?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:24.54,0:13:26.09,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在系统面板的右上角\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}System panel, top right.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:49.40,0:13:50.78,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,乔西 当心点\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Josie, be careful.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:51.86,0:13:52.70,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}- Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:53.82,0:13:54.95,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好 你也是\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Yeah, you too.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:09.50,0:14:10.88,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,看到什么了吗 \N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}You see anything?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:12.05,0:14:13.43,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,他们在另一边 这里看不到\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}We're on the wrong side.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:14.13,0:14:16.97,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我们已经停了很长时间了 不是吗 \N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Well, we've been stopped for an awfully long time, haven't we?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:20.31,0:14:22.68,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,-机车 我们已下车了 -好 收到\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Engine, we're clear. - Okay. Copy.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:22.77,0:14:23.85,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,他们下车了 \N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}They're clear!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:23.94,0:14:25.69,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你能启动 加速到20吗 \N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}- Okay. Take us up to 20.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:31.23,0:14:33.03,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,悠着点 \N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}- Easy! Easy.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:02.72,0:15:04.60,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这是总的合并分类帐\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}- This is the general consolidated ledger.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:04.68,0:15:08.86,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,从中可以看到 司务长是在哪个环节 发现偷窃行为的\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}And you can see where the quartermaster detected pilfering.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:09.81,0:15:12.19,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,巧妙地分摊到了供应链的各个环节\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}- Cleverly dispersed along the supply chain.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:12.28,0:15:14.61,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是雷顿的余党干的\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}- Laytonites, or what's left of them.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:14.69,0:15:16.86,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,没错 有人在扮演罗宾汉呢\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}- Yeah. Someone's playing Robin Hood.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:20.12,0:15:23.29,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,扎拉 你感觉如何 \N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Zarah. Zarah. How are you feeling?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:23.37,0:15:28.08,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,-非常庞大 我挺好 谢谢关心 -很好…\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Enormous. - I'm fine, thank you. Oh, good.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:28.17,0:15:30.38,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哈维 我拿到了工程部的报告\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}- I have the engineering report, Javi.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:30.46,0:15:33.42,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,-给我吧 -我们来听她说吧\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}- I'll take that. - Let's hear it from her.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:33.51,0:15:35.59,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,扎拉 我很欣赏你传递坏消息的方式\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}I appreciate how you deliver bad news, Zarah.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:35.67,0:15:37.76,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你总能保持心明眼亮\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Always a clear-eyed view.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:39.14,0:15:40.05,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那好吧\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}- So, then,
Dialogue: 0,0:15:40.97,0:15:45.81,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,大部分二等车厢 和部分三等车厢的水管还冻着\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}your water pipes are still frozen. Most of Second and parts of Third.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:45.89,0:15:49.35,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,农业区的产量又下降了 不过本周只下降了6%\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}And Ag-Sec output is down again, but only by 6% this week.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:49.44,0:15:50.31,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这是因为有人盗窃…\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}- This is pilfering. I was--
Dialogue: 0,0:15:50.40,0:15:54.90,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,昨晚 43个休眠者 以及串连区的供热完全断了\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}- And last night, 43 sleepers and The Chains lost heat completely.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:54.99,0:15:57.57,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,仍有162名乘客处于疏散状态\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}162 passengers remain evacuated.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:57.65,0:15:59.61,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,如果我们没法同时为所有人供暖\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}- Well, if we can't keep them all warm at once,
Dialogue: 0,0:15:59.70,0:16:01.99,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那他们就得分批挨冻\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}they'll just have to be miserable in shifts.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:02.08,0:16:03.70,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,抛弃头等车厢呀\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}We'll cut First Class.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:04.41,0:16:05.41,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不行\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Out of the question.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:05.50,0:16:09.04,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,约瑟夫 你已经将其弃置 都空了 又结了冰 抛弃它可以减轻负担\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}- Well, you did decommission it, Joseph. It's empty and frozen. - Cut the weight.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:09.12,0:16:12.34,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,等我把机车和奥德丽夺回来之后 就会让头等车厢重现辉煌\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}- I will restore First to glory when I get my engine back-- and Audrey with it.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:12.42,0:16:16.72,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,也许有其他节约能源的方法 比如选择性宰杀\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}- Perhaps there's another way to conserve energy. - Like a cull.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:16.80,0:16:18.17,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不行 凯文 你这个食人魔\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}- No, Kevin, you ghoul.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:18.26,0:16:21.30,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,请教训一下他 提醒他这里是有规矩的\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}- Please berate him. Remind him there are rules.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:21.39,0:16:22.72,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,很抱歉得让你失望了 凯文\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Sorry to disappoint, Kevin.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:22.80,0:16:26.06,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,除了冻断一两根手臂 我们要尽可能保证大家活着\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}But minus an arm or two, we keep everyone as alive as possible
Dialogue: 0,0:16:26.14,0:16:28.98,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这样 奥德丽才能活着\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}so Audrey stays as alive as possible.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:29.06,0:16:31.10,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,-明白 -你也一样 亲爱的\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}- Of course. - And you too, my dear.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:32.98,0:16:34.32,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这是答应了的\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}- That's been guaranteed,
Dialogue: 0,0:16:35.53,0:16:36.78,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不是吗 \N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}hasn't it?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:39.74,0:16:40.91,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,再见 哈维\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Bye, Javi.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:43.70,0:16:44.66,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,规矩\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}- Rules.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:46.54,0:16:48.25,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,抵抗军可没这么规矩\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}The resistance is not so constrained.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:48.91,0:16:52.42,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,凯文 所有游戏都有规矩 有点创意嘛\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Every game has rules, Kevin. Get creative.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:31.50,0:17:32.79,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,军靴泰森\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Jackboot Tyson.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:32.87,0:17:34.63,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你到底能不能把我调出堆肥区 \N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}- Can you get me out of compost or not?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:34.71,0:17:35.96,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,再等一周\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}One more week.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:36.04,0:17:39.13,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不过 趁等的时候 洗个热水盆浴怎么样 \N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}But in the meantime, how about a nice hot bath?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:40.51,0:17:41.72,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你是在取笑我吗 \N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}You taking the piss?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:43.26,0:17:46.85,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,沐浴券 奖励你为抵抗事业作出的贡献\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Bathing token for services to the cause.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:53.06,0:17:54.81,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,凯文 要喝点什么吗 \N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}- What can we do for you, Kevin?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:56.23,0:17:57.23,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,给我来杯阿华田\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Ovaltine.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:57.32,0:18:00.40,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我们这里没有阿华田 只有列车自酿的烈酒\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Yeah, we don't have Ovaltine. We have train-made hooch.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:01.36,0:18:04.24,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好吧 来一杯那个酒\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}- Fine. One hooch.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:05.57,0:18:08.03,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,威尔福德先生很喜欢 你们打理这里的方式\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Mr. Wilford loves what you've done with the place,
Dialogue: 0,0:18:08.12,0:18:12.04,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不过 他需要你们多做一件事\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}but I'm afraid he needs just a smidge more from the deal.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:12.75,0:18:13.62,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,打听消息 \N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Information?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:16.46,0:18:21.17,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,抵抗军在不停地 各处讨好 盗取资源\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}- The subversives continue filching and currying favor
Dialogue: 0,0:18:21.97,0:18:24.59,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,而他们的首领 则不断从我们指缝里溜走\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}while their shot caller keeps slipping through our fingers.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:25.18,0:18:29.22,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我们现在希望能找出并抓住这个人\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}We would like this person identified and captured... now.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:32.23,0:18:34.35,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,也许喝醉的那个军靴知道点内幕\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}- Maybe our passed-out Jack knows something.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:36.98,0:18:38.15,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,军靴惠金斯 \N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Jackboot Whiggins?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:39.11,0:18:41.48,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嘿 斯图 \N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Oi, Stuie.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:41.57,0:18:44.32,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,-惠金斯 醒一醒 -干吗 \N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Wake up, Whiggins. - What?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:45.24,0:18:47.24,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你说我可以待在这里的\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}You said I could stay.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:48.45,0:18:50.58,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,-你是负责看守水资源的吧  -嗯 怎么了 \N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}- They put you on Water Security, yeah? Yes.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:50.66,0:18:53.54,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你以前是头等车厢的 所以你会乐意帮忙的\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}- You're a former Firstie, so you'll be glad to help.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:53.62,0:18:56.12,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,水资源的安全出了什么问题 \N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}- Well, what's happening in Water Security?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:59.54,0:19:00.88,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,没有问题啊\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Uh, you know, nothing.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:02.42,0:19:03.46,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:04.84,0:19:05.72,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好吧…\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Um, well,
Dialogue: 0,0:19:07.09,0:19:08.64,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,只是很小的问题\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}you know, very little.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:10.31,0:19:12.97,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,-凯文需要的不多 -只需要一点线索就行\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Kevin doesn't need much. - Just a little thread to pick.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:13.68,0:19:14.56,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,说吧\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Come on.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:15.98,0:19:19.48,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好吧 我听说二等车厢的配水员\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}- Well, I've heard that the Second Class Watermaster
Dialogue: 0,0:19:19.56,0:19:21.23,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在给为抵抗军效力的人…\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}was giving away hot baths
Dialogue: 0,0:19:23.44,0:19:25.11,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,提供免费热水盆浴\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}for service to the resistance.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:27.36,0:19:28.28,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我们来看看\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Let's have a look.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:32.91,0:19:34.45,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,伤口恢复得很不错\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Oh, that's healing nicely.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:34.54,0:19:36.25,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你今天涂药膏了吗 \N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Have you applied your cream today?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:37.75,0:19:39.71,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,-没有 先生 -那就让我来帮你涂吧\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}- No, sir. - Well, then allow me.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:48.22,0:19:51.35,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,没事的 乖狗狗 没事的 躺下\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Oh, it's all right, cub. It's all right. You like me now.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:52.89,0:19:55.06,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,朱庇特的事\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}This business with Jupiter.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:55.14,0:19:58.35,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哈维尔 我知道 用它对付人的手法很粗暴\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}I know she's a blunt tool, Javier.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:58.44,0:20:03.23,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,可是 当你一个人 得为近三千人负责时\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}But when you're one man responsible for nearly 3,000...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:04.86,0:20:07.11,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,光是纪律严明是不够的\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}It's not enough being a disciplinarian.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:07.20,0:20:09.66,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我得再用上别的手段才行\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}You need to add a little chaos to the mix.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:10.41,0:20:11.91,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在这里 就是朱庇特\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}In here, it's Jupiter.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:11.99,0:20:15.20,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在外面 就是凯文 咬牙切齿 横冲直撞\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Out there, it's Kevin, gnashing his teeth and running amok.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:17.00,0:20:19.58,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哈维尔 你无法与不可预测的事情作对\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}You can't fight the unpredictable, Javier.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:20.83,0:20:22.38,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这就是我确保大家安全的方法\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}That's how I keep everyone safe.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:23.13,0:20:23.96,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,总之\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Anyway...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:25.26,0:20:27.59,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我希望你能看清问题的本质\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}I hope you see it for what it is.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:30.59,0:20:32.30,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我确实很需要你 哈维尔\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}I do need you, Javier.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:38.85,0:20:39.69,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好小伙子\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Good man.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:45.78,0:20:46.94,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我是威尔福德\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Wilford.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:47.03,0:20:48.95,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,先生 我们有线索了\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Sir, we have a lead.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:11.13,0:21:14.47,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,配水员阿诺多雷耶斯\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Watermaster Arnoldo Reyas.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:18.47,0:21:19.98,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,永恒机车永不停歇\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}- Sí, señor. The Engine will provide.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:25.98,0:21:27.19,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,清新如洗\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Clean as a baby.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:37.20,0:21:38.20,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,来吧\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Come on.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:39.33,0:21:41.08,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,出来吧 别着凉了\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Come on out before you get cold.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:47.59,0:21:49.17,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,配水员把我们的位置告诉了他们\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}- The Watermaster told them where we are.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:49.26,0:21:51.17,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,-得换地方了 -又要换 \N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}- Gotta go. - Again.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:00.98,0:22:02.02,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,-好了吗  -好了\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}- Okay. - Okay.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:02.10,0:22:03.31,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,-来吧 -来了\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}- Come on. - I'm coming.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:03.39,0:22:04.44,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这就对了 就是这样\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}- There you go, that's it.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:06.31,0:22:09.07,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不 我们走吧 快\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}- Oh. - No, no, no, no, no, no. Ruth, let's go, quick. Quick, quick, quick, quick, quick.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:09.15,0:22:10.94,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,知道了 \N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}- All right. All right.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:11.03,0:22:13.11,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不是所有人都像你行动这么迅速\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}We can't all be built like a bloody whippet.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:22.12,0:22:23.54,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,来吧\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Come on. Come on.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:29.21,0:22:30.21,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我们得走了\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}We gotta go!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:39.76,0:22:41.02,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,走吧\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}- Let's go. Let's go!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:06.21,0:23:09.21,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,终点站到了 当然 这里都结冰了 通勤车不能通行\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}End of the line. The First is too frozen for the subtrain.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:13.09,0:23:13.92,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Okay.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:17.26,0:23:19.35,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,天啊 这里真冷\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Crikey, it's cold.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:19.43,0:23:21.39,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好 等一下\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Just wait.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:33.40,0:23:36.11,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,他们在这里待过 就在我们的眼皮底下\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}- They were here. Right under our noses.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:37.66,0:23:38.53,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,背信弃义\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Treachery.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:40.87,0:23:41.87,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你个机灵鬼\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}- Who are you,
Dialogue: 0,0:23:43.20,0:23:44.45,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你是谁 \N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}you clever thing?
Dialogue: 0,0:23:46.16,0:23:49.71,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,他们把这里的供热调得很低 一直都在零下25度\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}- They got it on trickle, stays around minus 25.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:50.25,0:23:54.55,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我希望他们不会找到这里来 因为这里太冷 没法生活\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}I'm hoping they won't look back here, because, you know, it's too cold to live.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:04.18,0:24:05.22,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我的天\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Oh, my God.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:06.98,0:24:10.35,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎么 凯文就不能把这里收拾一下 \N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}What, Kevin couldn't put anything away?
Dialogue: 0,0:24:12.57,0:24:13.86,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,鲁丝 在这里面\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}In here, Ruth.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:18.74,0:24:19.99,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,当心头\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Watch your head.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:30.12,0:24:33.34,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我找了几个同志替你布置了一下\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Had a couple of our comrades gussy it up for ya.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:33.42,0:24:35.55,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,看 零下12度\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}See, minus 12.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:36.26,0:24:38.34,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真不错 谢谢你\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}- It's lovely, thank you. - Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:38.42,0:24:40.09,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,替我转达一下谢意\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}- Send my regards down the line.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:41.68,0:24:42.51,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎么了 \N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}- What?
Dialogue: 0,0:24:43.76,0:24:46.39,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你喜欢我这机灵的身板吗 \N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}What, you likey that I'm built like a whippet?
Dialogue: 0,0:24:46.47,0:24:49.14,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,什么呀 放尊重点\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}- No. Mind your cheek.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:51.69,0:24:53.40,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,-谢谢你 -不客气\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}- Thank you. - You're welcome.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:59.65,0:25:01.45,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,雷顿先生 如果你在外面\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}- If you're out there, Mr. Layton,
Dialogue: 0,0:25:02.66,0:25:04.78,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,现在是回来的好时机\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}now would be a great time to come home.
Dialogue: 0,0:25:35.48,0:25:36.61,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,雪国列车 \N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}"Snowpiercer,"
Dialogue: 0,0:25:38.44,0:25:40.86,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,雪国列车 收到请回答\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}come in. "Snowpiercer."
Dialogue: 0,0:25:45.49,0:25:46.49,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,糟糕\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Oh, shit.
Dialogue: 0,0:25:46.58,0:25:47.99,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,（温度：14度 剩余8分钟）
Dialogue: 0,0:25:48.08,0:25:49.25,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嘿 伙计\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Hey, buddy.
Dialogue: 0,0:25:54.21,0:25:55.33,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你带上冲浪板了吗 \N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}You bring your surfboard?
Dialogue: 0,0:25:56.04,0:25:58.05,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我想着还是改滑雪橇的好\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}- Thought we'd do some sledding instead.
Dialogue: 0,0:25:58.13,0:26:00.51,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,兄弟 你的防护服还能撑多久 \N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Hey, what's your suit at, man?
Dialogue: 0,0:26:01.09,0:26:02.47,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,7分45秒\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}- 7:45.
Dialogue: 0,0:26:03.84,0:26:04.84,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,机车怎么样了 \N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}The Engine.
Dialogue: 0,0:26:04.93,0:26:08.39,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,别为机车操心 艾莉在处理呢 本 你有哪里疼吗 \N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}- Don't worry about the Engine. Alex is on it. Where are you hurting, Ben?
Dialogue: 0,0:26:09.31,0:26:10.73,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,胸口有点疼\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Bit of pain in the chest.
Dialogue: 0,0:26:10.81,0:26:12.35,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,手指和脚趾能动吗 \N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}- Can you move your fingers and toes?
Dialogue: 0,0:26:13.85,0:26:14.94,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,很好\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}- All right.
Dialogue: 0,0:26:15.02,0:26:17.44,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,-我这就下去 -太危险了 雷顿\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}I'm coming down. - Too risky, Layton.
Dialogue: 0,0:26:17.52,0:26:19.15,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,放根绳子下来…\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Send down a rope.
Dialogue: 0,0:26:19.23,0:26:21.82,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你别操心了 你等着 我马上回来\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}- Oh, man. Don't worry about it. You sit tight, man. I'll be right back.
Dialogue: 0,0:26:24.70,0:26:25.82,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,他们在排放燃料 \N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}They're venting?
Dialogue: 0,0:26:26.74,0:26:29.79,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,他们只是在缓缓前进 给引擎降温 我不明白为什么要这样做\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}They're just rolling fast enough to cool down. - I don't--I don't get it.
Dialogue: 0,0:26:29.87,0:26:32.08,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,-我明白 -我觉得他们没回来\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}- I do. - I don't think they got back on.
Dialogue: 0,0:26:32.87,0:26:35.29,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,-你在说什么呢  -都有谁在外面 \N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}What are you talking about? - So who's outside?
Dialogue: 0,0:26:35.79,0:26:38.13,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我不知道 你觉得他们有事会告诉我吗 \N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}- I don't know. You think they tell me anything?
Dialogue: 0,0:26:38.21,0:26:39.59,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我知道本之前下车了\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}I know Ben went out.
Dialogue: 0,0:26:40.09,0:26:42.09,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我从我房间的窗口 看到另有两个人下去了\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}- Yeah, well, I think I saw two more from my window.
Dialogue: 0,0:26:42.17,0:26:45.63,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那准是艾莉在驾驶列车 她抛弃他们了吗 \N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}- Well, then Alex has to be driving. Did she ditch them?
Dialogue: 0,0:26:46.59,0:26:50.10,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,-他们没接电话 -马汀 是时候了\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}They're not answering. Martin, it's time.
Dialogue: 0,0:26:52.14,0:26:56.02,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,行 好 那提尔怎么办 \N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Yeah. Okay. What about Till?
Dialogue: 0,0:26:56.10,0:26:58.94,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我们只能先去机车 看情况再说\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}- Well, we'll just have to go to the Engine and find out.
Dialogue: 0,0:26:59.02,0:26:59.94,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这是怎么回事 \N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}What's happening?
Dialogue: 0,0:27:00.02,0:27:02.23,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我们得回去跟另一列列车汇合\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}We have to get back with the other train.
Dialogue: 0,0:27:02.78,0:27:06.32,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,如果你帮忙 我就不告诉威尔福德 你很配合他们的事\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Help us, and I won't tell Wilford you've been cooperating.
Dialogue: 0,0:27:07.57,0:27:09.16,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你不是认真的吧 \N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Are you serious right now?
Dialogue: 0,0:27:12.08,0:27:13.08,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,绝对认真\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}- Deadly serious.
Dialogue: 0,0:27:13.16,0:27:16.08,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我们必须重新连接 好吗  我们这都是在干什么 \N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Look, we need to reconnect. Okay? What are we doing out here?
Dialogue: 0,0:27:16.17,0:27:18.92,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我们在漫无目的地瞎转悠 我们快没食物了\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}- Yeah, we've been running around aimlessly. We're running out of food.
Dialogue: 0,0:27:19.75,0:27:20.84,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,最后一次机会\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Last chance.
Dialogue: 0,0:27:22.42,0:27:23.80,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,要么回到威尔福德身边\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Get back with Wilford
Dialogue: 0,0:27:25.13,0:27:26.84,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,要么就给雷顿陪葬\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}or dig a grave with Layton.
Dialogue: 0,0:27:31.47,0:27:32.81,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那就进牢房去\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Then get in the cage.
Dialogue: 0,0:27:51.16,0:27:52.45,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,现在的时速是多少 \N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}What's our speed?
Dialogue: 0,0:27:53.37,0:27:56.04,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,-75公里 -好 我们交换一下\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Um, 75. - Okay, let's switch places;
Dialogue: 0,0:27:56.12,0:27:58.83,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我起动冷却程序时 你得待在这里\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}I need you over here while I start the cooling sequence.
Dialogue: 0,0:27:59.42,0:28:01.00,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你得给这些电线配对\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Okay, you're gonna match these lines.
Dialogue: 0,0:28:01.09,0:28:04.09,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,蓝色接蓝色 红色接红色 诸如此类 明白了吗 \N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Blue to blue, red to red, and so on, you got it?
Dialogue: 0,0:28:04.17,0:28:05.05,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,明白\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}- Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:28:05.13,0:28:07.34,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,制动员 你得确定哦 这些线是带电的\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}- Be sure, Brakeman, okay? - These currents are live.
Dialogue: 0,0:28:07.43,0:28:09.59,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,确定 对颜色嘛 我能行 换吧\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}- Yeah, match the colors. I got it. Let's go.
Dialogue: 0,0:28:12.72,0:28:14.39,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,还有 我不是该死的制动员\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}And I'm not a freaking Brakeman.
Dialogue: 0,0:28:20.94,0:28:21.81,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嘿\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Hey.
Dialogue: 0,0:28:23.02,0:28:23.86,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嘿 \N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Hey!
Dialogue: 0,0:28:25.44,0:28:28.57,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,万一他们问起来 就说是你逼我放你出来的\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Okay, well, just in case they ask, you forced me to let you out.
Dialogue: 0,0:28:53.68,0:28:54.60,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好了
Dialogue: 0,0:29:12.99,0:29:14.12,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,伙计 还剩多少时间 \N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}- Hey. Time?
Dialogue: 0,0:29:16.54,0:29:17.75,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,2分钟\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}- Two minutes.
Dialogue: 0,0:29:17.83,0:29:22.33,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好 别担心 兄弟 有足够的时间\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}- All right, not to worry, brother. There's plenty to go around.
Dialogue: 0,0:29:23.79,0:29:25.38,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不多了 雷顿\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Not too much, Layton.
Dialogue: 0,0:29:26.13,0:29:27.76,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,别弄得咱俩都没时间了\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Let's not both run out.
Dialogue: 0,0:29:28.88,0:29:29.88,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Hey.
Dialogue: 0,0:29:34.39,0:29:38.97,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嘿 你之前说冲浪的事 你真的冲过浪 \N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Hey, hey. All that surf stuff you talking, you really do that?
Dialogue: 0,0:29:40.10,0:29:41.02,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,本奈特\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Bennet.
Dialogue: 0,0:29:43.23,0:29:44.40,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,-冲浪的事  -对\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}- Surfing? - Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:29:45.77,0:29:52.70,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我16岁时 在索佩拉纳待过一个夏天\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Yeah, I spent a summer in Sopelana when I was 16.
Dialogue: 0,0:29:53.66,0:29:57.08,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,当地人会冲一种叫“马路牙子”的浪\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Yeah, the locals surfed a wave called El Bordillo.
Dialogue: 0,0:29:57.16,0:29:59.37,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,-是吗  -是的\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}- Oh, yeah? - Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:30:00.04,0:30:03.75,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我在那浪尖上学到的 比大学七年学的都多\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}I learned more on that wave than in seven years of university.
Dialogue: 0,0:30:06.25,0:30:07.17,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你后来回去过吗 \N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}You ever go back?
Dialogue: 0,0:30:08.75,0:30:11.09,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯 回去过一次\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Yeah, once.
Dialogue: 0,0:30:12.84,0:30:15.64,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,-再去的时候 海平面已上升… -好\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}By then, the rising sea levels
Dialogue: 0,0:30:16.14,0:30:17.81,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,…改变了海岸线\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}changed the coastline.
Dialogue: 0,0:30:18.64,0:30:19.93,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,海浪没有了\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}The wave was gone.
Dialogue: 0,0:30:24.14,0:30:25.65,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我们该往回开了吧 \N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}- Shouldn't we start going back?
Dialogue: 0,0:30:26.40,0:30:27.48,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,空燃比还是太低\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}We're still too rich.
Dialogue: 0,0:30:27.57,0:30:30.15,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,-那要等多久  -我不知道 \N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}- Well, how long? - I don't--I don't know.
Dialogue: 0,0:30:30.23,0:30:34.20,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嘿 艾莉 你能处理好的\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}- Hey, hey, hey, hey, Alex, you can do this.
Dialogue: 0,0:30:34.28,0:30:35.70,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,-好吗  -我不行\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}- Okay? - I can't.
Dialogue: 0,0:30:38.08,0:30:39.49,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,如果换作梅兰妮 她会怎么做 \N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}What would Melanie do?
Dialogue: 0,0:30:41.08,0:30:43.54,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,她会直接知道答案\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}- She would just know the answer. That's what she would do.
Dialogue: 0,0:30:43.62,0:30:44.58,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好吧 那…\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Okay, fine, then.
Dialogue: 0,0:30:46.08,0:30:47.59,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,如果换了是本呢 \N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}What would--What would Ben do?
Dialogue: 0,0:30:47.67,0:30:50.46,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,他会拿上纸和笔 边画边解释给你听\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}- He would grab a pen and paper and start mansplaining.
Dialogue: 0,0:30:50.55,0:30:53.42,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好 很好 那就大声把问题列出来吧\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}- Okay, good. Just--just talk it out, then.
Dialogue: 0,0:30:59.89,0:31:02.10,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,当初设计这引擎 是为了在负载下高速行驶\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}- Built to work at speed, under load,
Dialogue: 0,0:31:02.89,0:31:04.10,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但我们既没负载也没速度\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}but we have neither.
Dialogue: 0,0:31:04.77,0:31:07.23,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,它成了被困在玩具车上的喷气发动机\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}We're a jet engine strapped to a toy wagon.
Dialogue: 0,0:31:08.02,0:31:09.77,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我们只需急刹车两次\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}All we have to do is stop on a dime
Dialogue: 0,0:31:09.86,0:31:13.07,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,确保不抛锚 也不耗尽燃料 其中一次反向即可\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}without stalling or burning up twice and once in reverse.
Dialogue: 0,0:31:15.28,0:31:18.16,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,提尔 我们有三分钟的时间 可以倒回去接他们\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}All right, Till, there's a three-minute window to reverse back to them.
Dialogue: 0,0:31:18.24,0:31:19.91,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你一直在躲着我吗 \N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Have you been avoiding me?
Dialogue: 0,0:31:22.95,0:31:25.21,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我让他们把你关在冷藏室里\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}- I told them to lock you in the meat locker.
Dialogue: 0,0:31:25.96,0:31:28.96,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,他们觉得关在图书馆更安全 如今看来 安全个屁\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}They thought the library was more secure. So much for that.
Dialogue: 0,0:31:29.54,0:31:30.54,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,他们都在外面吗 \N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Are they all outside?
Dialogue: 0,0:31:30.63,0:31:32.34,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,奥德丽 我现在有点忙\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}- I'm a bit busy right now, Audrey.
Dialogue: 0,0:31:32.42,0:31:33.46,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我能看得出来\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Well, I can see that.
Dialogue: 0,0:31:39.30,0:31:42.64,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,看呀 看看我有什么\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Look. Look. Look, what I have.
Dialogue: 0,0:31:43.22,0:31:44.18,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,看啊\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Look!
Dialogue: 0,0:31:45.18,0:31:47.60,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,他们抓我当人质时 它就在我身上了\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}I had it on me when they took me hostage.
Dialogue: 0,0:31:48.35,0:31:51.94,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我等了六个月 就为了这一刻\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}I have been waiting six months for this moment.
Dialogue: 0,0:32:02.03,0:32:05.33,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,现在 让我们谈谈 回去找“爹地”的事吧\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Now let's talk about going home to Daddy.
Dialogue: 0,0:32:43.66,0:32:46.37,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,抓紧了 我们到上面见 乔西 开始拉吧\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}- Hold on tight, buddy. I'll see you up there. - Josie, let's go.
Dialogue: 0,0:32:50.92,0:32:52.00,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好了 本\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}All right, Ben.
Dialogue: 0,0:33:19.65,0:33:20.74,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,可以了\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Here you go.
Dialogue: 0,0:33:21.66,0:33:24.37,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好 本 就差一点了 成了\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}All right. Nearly there, Ben. Nearly there. There, it's done.
Dialogue: 0,0:33:25.41,0:33:27.24,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你上来了 好了\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Over the edge, that's it.
Dialogue: 0,0:33:29.50,0:33:32.08,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,乔西 把开关扔给我 把他送回去\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}- Josie, throw me the switch and start back with him.
Dialogue: 0,0:33:32.17,0:33:36.09,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,-不行 你不上来 我们不走 -他快不行了 快走 我会赶上的\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}- No, not till you're out of there. He's fading, Josie. Get going. I'll catch up.
Dialogue: 0,0:33:41.55,0:33:44.09,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,-你的防护服还能撑多久  -足够久 别担心\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}What's your suit at? - Plenty. Don't worry about it.
Dialogue: 0,0:33:45.05,0:33:46.18,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我随后就回去\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}I'm right behind you.
Dialogue: 0,0:33:47.93,0:33:48.93,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好了\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Okay.
Dialogue: 0,0:34:05.78,0:34:08.87,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,（防护服温度：11度 剩余时间：7分21秒）
Dialogue: 0,0:35:29.74,0:35:31.45,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,（注意：辐射区 污染区）
Dialogue: 0,0:35:40.21,0:35:41.21,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,有人吗 \N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Hello.
Dialogue: 0,0:35:43.76,0:35:47.38,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,（防护服温度：9度 剩余时间：4分39秒）
Dialogue: 0,0:36:30.26,0:36:31.39,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,有人吗 \N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Hello?
Dialogue: 0,0:37:12.30,0:37:13.55,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,雷顿 收到请回答 雷顿\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Layton, come in, Layton.
Dialogue: 0,0:37:15.39,0:37:17.18,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,雷顿 快回答 雷顿\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Layton, come in, Layton.
Dialogue: 0,0:37:42.75,0:37:45.13,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,（防护服温度：零下12度 剩余时间：0分0秒）
Dialogue: 0,0:37:49.76,0:37:51.17,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你妈死了 艾莉\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}- Your mother didn't make it, Alex.
Dialogue: 0,0:37:51.88,0:37:56.72,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,外面有绿洲的那个想法 也随她而去了\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}And that idea of an oasis out there died with her.
Dialogue: 0,0:37:56.81,0:37:58.02,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,没有随她而去\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}No, it hasn't.
Dialogue: 0,0:37:59.31,0:38:01.98,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我觉得如果你们发现了什么的话\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}- Well, I think you would all be getting along much better
Dialogue: 0,0:38:02.06,0:38:03.60,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你们几个的关系会好很多\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}if you discovered anything.
Dialogue: 0,0:38:03.69,0:38:05.98,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你根本不知道我们发现了什么\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}- Well, you have no idea what we've discovered.
Dialogue: 0,0:38:20.45,0:38:22.79,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,威尔福德有解决方法 艾莉\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}- Wilford has the answers, Alex.
Dialogue: 0,0:38:24.83,0:38:28.34,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,继续开 就能解决一切问题\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Just keep going, and you solve everything.
Dialogue: 0,0:38:30.88,0:38:34.89,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,继续开就是\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Just keep going.
Dialogue: 0,0:38:55.61,0:38:57.12,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不 不要 \N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}No, don't.
Dialogue: 0,0:38:57.20,0:38:58.28,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,离她远点\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Get away from her.
Dialogue: 0,0:39:00.70,0:39:02.45,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,艾莉 我们得回去\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Alex, you gotta go back.
Dialogue: 0,0:39:02.54,0:39:04.87,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,往前开 艾莉 回他那里去\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}- Ahead, Alex. Back home to him.
Dialogue: 0,0:39:04.96,0:39:06.08,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我们不能把他们丢在外面\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}- We can't leave them out there.
Dialogue: 0,0:39:06.17,0:39:08.50,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,什么烂好人 艾莉 别听她的\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}- Don't listen to her bleeding heart, Alex.
Dialogue: 0,0:39:08.59,0:39:10.59,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,学一学约瑟夫 算算存活率\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Just do the calculus of survival like Joseph would.
Dialogue: 0,0:39:10.67,0:39:12.71,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,够了 你们俩都闭嘴 \N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}- Stop! Both of you, just stop!
Dialogue: 0,0:39:13.55,0:39:14.38,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,见鬼 \N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Shit.
Dialogue: 0,0:39:16.30,0:39:17.68,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,只管继续往前开 \N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Just go ahead!
Dialogue: 0,0:39:26.65,0:39:29.48,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,艾莉\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Alex.
Dialogue: 0,0:39:29.56,0:39:32.03,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,-把列车停下 -万一她是对的怎么办 \N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Alex, stop the train. What if she was right?
Dialogue: 0,0:39:32.78,0:39:34.86,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,-万一威尔福德是最好的选择呢  -他不是\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}What if Wilford is the best bet? - He's not.
Dialogue: 0,0:39:35.36,0:39:36.45,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,梅兰妮才是\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Melanie is.
Dialogue: 0,0:39:37.11,0:39:39.95,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好吗 我们可以熬过这一关的 艾莉\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Okay? We can get through this, Alex.
Dialogue: 0,0:39:40.95,0:39:42.33,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,别选错了方向\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Don't tip it the wrong way.
Dialogue: 0,0:39:44.25,0:39:46.21,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好吗 好\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Okay? Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:40:18.95,0:40:21.28,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,（防护服温度 零下38度 充电中）
Dialogue: 0,0:41:02.03,0:41:03.78,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,雪国列车 收到请回答 雪国列车\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}- "Snowpiercer." Come in, "Snowpiercer."
Dialogue: 0,0:41:08.33,0:41:10.12,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,雷顿 你听到了吗 \N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Layton, Layton, can you read me?
Dialogue: 0,0:41:11.75,0:41:13.04,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,雷顿 \N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Layton.
Dialogue: 0,0:41:15.17,0:41:16.63,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,雪国列车 收到请回答\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}"Snowpiercer," come in.
Dialogue: 0,0:41:18.67,0:41:19.76,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,糟糕\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Shit.
Dialogue: 0,0:41:20.80,0:41:23.18,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在那里 他们在那里\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}There. There they are.
Dialogue: 0,0:41:24.68,0:41:26.68,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我只看到两个人 只有两个人\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}There's only two-- there's only two of them.
Dialogue: 0,0:41:32.52,0:41:37.86,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,起来 本 起来
Dialogue: 0,0:41:43.99,0:41:46.20,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,-等一下 我的胸部 -坐在那里\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}- Wait, wait. - Sit there.
Dialogue: 0,0:41:53.75,0:41:55.21,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,雷顿 收到请回答 雷顿\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Layton, come in, Layton.
Dialogue: 0,0:41:57.96,0:41:58.84,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,雷顿 \N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Layton,
Dialogue: 0,0:41:58.92,0:42:00.17,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,雷顿 收到请回答\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}come in, Layton.
Dialogue: 0,0:42:03.18,0:42:04.89,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,听着 我会回来的 好吗 \N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Look, I'll be back, okay?
Dialogue: 0,0:42:04.97,0:42:07.22,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,乔西 你在外面待得太久了\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}- Josie, you've been out too long.
Dialogue: 0,0:42:08.39,0:42:10.48,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我能找到他的 我去去就回\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}- I can find him. I'll be back.
Dialogue: 0,0:42:10.56,0:42:14.94,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,乔西 他的防护服五分钟前就没电了\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}- Josie, his suit ran out five minutes ago.
Dialogue: 0,0:42:26.16,0:42:29.62,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,雷顿\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Layton. Layton!
Dialogue: 0,0:42:31.96,0:42:33.46,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎么了 \N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}- What? What?
Dialogue: 0,0:42:34.29,0:42:37.84,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,-他在外面吗 他在吗  -是的 他在\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}He's there? - Yes. - He's there? He's there.
Dialogue: 0,0:43:07.28,0:43:10.37,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你想要什么 \N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}So what can I get you?
Dialogue: 0,0:43:11.12,0:43:13.62,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我会说 我想要的一切我都有了\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}- I'd say I've got everything I ever wanted.
Dialogue: 0,0:43:13.71,0:43:14.79,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,一个女朋友\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}A girl,
Dialogue: 0,0:43:16.29,0:43:17.58,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,一间夜总会\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}a club,
Dialogue: 0,0:43:17.67,0:43:20.42,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,还有伟大的威尔福德先生的感激\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}and the gratitude of the great Mr. Wilford.
Dialogue: 0,0:43:22.30,0:43:23.21,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,过来\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Come on.
Dialogue: 0,0:43:29.30,0:43:31.47,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,谁不想洗个舒适的热水澡呢 \N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}- Wouldn't we all love a nice warm bath?
Dialogue: 0,0:43:32.89,0:43:38.15,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这两个家伙为了抵抗军 从你们这里窃取了热水\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}These two stole hot water resources from you for the resistance.
Dialogue: 0,0:43:38.98,0:43:40.57,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,因为他们要干净…\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Because they had to be clean...
Dialogue: 0,0:43:40.65,0:43:42.98,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,（道路 真理 我们的生存方式）
Dialogue: 0,0:43:43.07,0:43:43.90,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,…你们就没澡洗了\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}You go unwashed.
Dialogue: 0,0:43:45.11,0:43:46.32,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你先来\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}You first.
Dialogue: 0,0:43:59.17,0:44:00.21,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,没事的\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}It's all right.
Dialogue: 0,0:44:01.63,0:44:02.67,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那是值得的\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}It was worth it.
Dialogue: 0,0:44:26.44,0:44:29.41,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我也不想错过公开羞辱的仪式\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}- Well, I hate to miss a public defiling,
Dialogue: 0,0:44:29.49,0:44:32.66,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但仪式早就开始多时了吧 \N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}but the proceedings are rather foregone, aren't they?
Dialogue: 0,0:44:34.62,0:44:38.29,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我更愿意和朋友们 一起在这里 踏上一条新的征程\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}I'd much rather be here with my friends, embarking on a fresh path.
Dialogue: 0,0:46:15.18,0:46:20.18,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,字幕翻译： 黛拉

